msgid ""
"Multisig accounts are editable at the blockchain level. In this case, we "
"want to make both cosignatories required, shifting to a 2-of-2 multisig "
"instead. You can achieve this by increasing ``minApproval`` parameter in "
"one unit."
msgstr ""
"Multisig帐户可在区块链级别进行编辑。 在这种情况下，我们希望使两个cosignatories都需要参与决定，转而使用2-of-2 "
"multisig。 我们可以通过在一个单元中增加``minApproval``参数来实现它。"

