msgid "2-of-2 multisig account example"
msgstr "2-of-2 multisig帐户示例"

#: ../../source/guides/account/modifying-a-multisig-account.rst:61
msgid ""
"One of the accounts, for example Alice's, announces a :ref:`modify "
"multisig account transaction <modify-multisig-account-transaction>` "
"wrapped in an :ref:`aggregate transaction <aggregate-transaction>`, "
"increasing ``minApprovalDelta``."
msgstr ""
"其中一个帐户，例如Alice的，宣布:ref:`修改multisig帐户交易<modify-multisig-account-"
"transaction>`保存在:ref:`aggregate transaction <aggregate-"
"transaction>`中，增加``minApprovalDelta``。"

#: ../../source/guides/account/modifying-a-multisig-account.rst:63
msgid ""
"Create a modify multisig account transaction, increasing minAprovalDelta "
"in one unit."
msgstr "创建修改multisig帐户交易，在一个单元中增加minAprovalDelta。"

#: ../../source/guides/account/modifying-a-multisig-account.rst:82
msgid ""
"Wrap the modify multisig account transaction under an aggregate "
"transaction, attaching multisig public key as the signer."
msgstr "在聚合交易下包装修改multisig帐户交易，签名者将multisig公钥附加到交易。"

#: ../../source/guides/account/modifying-a-multisig-account.rst:84
msgid ""
"An aggregate transaction is *complete* if, before announcing it to the "
"network, all required cosignatories have signed it. If valid, it will be "
"included in a block."
msgstr "在向网络宣布所有必需的签名者已经签署交易之前，汇总交易的状态是*complete*。 如果交易有效，它将被保存在一个块中。"

#: ../../source/guides/account/modifying-a-multisig-account.rst:86
msgid ""
"As only one cosignature is required (1-of-2), Alice can sign the "
"transaction and announce it to the network."
msgstr "由于只需要一个共同签名（1-of-2），Alice可以签署交易并将其通知给网络。"

#: ../../source/guides/account/modifying-a-multisig-account.rst:105
msgid ""
"Once confirmed, the minApproval value of the multisig will be set to 2, "
"having our 2-of-2 multisig."
msgstr "确认后，multisig的minApproval值将设置为2，2-of-2 multisig产生了。"

#: ../../source/guides/account/modifying-a-multisig-account.rst:107
msgid ""
"If you want to decrease the minApproval parameter, going back to a 1-of-2"
" multisig, set minApprovalDelta with a negative value. In this case "
"``-1``."
msgstr "如果要减小minApproval参数，返回1-of-2 multisig，请将minApprovalDelta设置为负值。 比如``-1``。"

